    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S) In nomine dei eterni, breve ad memoriam habendam qualiter factum est
                        presentibus personis quas inferius nominabimus. <persName><name
                                ref="Agelinda">Ailina</name></persName> relicta quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Gherardus/Mascarellus">Ierardini
                                Mascarelli</name></persName>, propterea quia cognovit plenam
                        voluntatem suprascripti quondam viri sui Ierardini, offerrendo beati
                            <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/3206" key="#Hospitals"><rs
                                key="#Hospitals">hospitali</rs> qui vocatur <placeName
                                key="#Hospitals" ref="#places/3207">Teupasscio</placeName></orgName>
                        unam integram <rs key="#Petiae">petiam</rs> de terra cum multis arboribus et
                        omni hedificio super se habente que est posita in loco qui vocatur
                            <placeName key="#Petiae" ref="#places/3228">Ultrario</placeName>, iuxta
                        Filangnore, que fuit recta et hedificata per quondam massaium nomine
                                <persName><name ref="Berno">Bernum</name></persName>. Postquam
                        predictus Ierardinus preocupatus fuit subitanea morte, tunc suprascripta
                        Ailina uxor in ipsa die obitus sui mariti, cum consilio et consensu
                                <persName><name ref="Formentus">Formentini</name></persName>
                        mundualdi sui et aliorum multorum vicinorum parentum, pro remedio anime sue
                        et suprascripti Ierardini, per virgam quam in suas manibus tenebat, dedit et
                        tradidit deo et predicti <orgName key="#Bridges/pontoons #Hospitals"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3209">hospitali et <rs key="#Bridges/pontoons"
                                >ponti</rs> de Arno</orgName>, in manibus <rs key="#Priests"
                            >presbiteri</rs>
                        <persName key="#Priests"><name ref="Iohannes">Iohanni</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Montanus">Montanini</name></persName> in vice
                        domini <persName><name ref="Wido">Guidonis</name></persName> rectoris
                        predicti hospitali et ponti videlicet integram prenominatam petiam de terra
                        cum integriss omnibus arboribus super se et infra se habente (…).
                            <foreign>Pena</foreign>: argienti optimi sol. quatuor centum.
                            <foreign>Maledizioni</foreign>. Hoc factum est in loco qui vocatur
                            <placeName ref="#places/319">Cappiano</placeName>, in presentia et
                        testimonio <persName><name ref="Hubertus">Ubertinotti</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Vecchio">Vechii</name></persName> filii quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Heinricus">Henrichi</name></persName>, et
                                <persName><name ref="Forestanus">Forestani</name></persName> filii
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Gherardus">Ierardini</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Hugolinus">Ugolinelli</name></persName> filii
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Grassus">Grasi</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Gotefredus">Gottifredi</name></persName> filii
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Brunus">Brunonis</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Wilielmus">Guilgielmini</name></persName> filii
                        quondam Aldel(…) et <persName><name ref="Ardoinus">Arduini</name></persName>
                        filii quondam <persName><name ref="Wilielmus">Guilgielmi</name></persName>
                        et aliorum plurimum: <persName><name ref="Borgognone"
                            >Borgongnonis</name></persName> quondam <persName><name ref="Pungilio"
                                >Pungilion</name>(…)</persName>, <persName><name ref="Maragone"
                                >Maragonis</name></persName> et <persName><name ref="Bernardus"
                                >Bernardini</name></persName> filii quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Ficarellus">Ficarelli</name></persName>, omnes predicti rogati
                            <rs key="#Witness">testes</rs>. Anno dominice incarnationis millesimo
                        centesimo quinquagesimo octavo, septimo kalendas iunii, indictione sexta.
                        (S) <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Hubertus"
                            >Hubertus</name></persName> donni inperatoris <rs key="#Notary"
                            >notharius</rs> ibi fui et hoc breve scripsi. </ab>
